  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <p xml:id="NA178-kiḷavi">itu ciṟaippuṟamākat tōḻi ceṟippaṟivuṟīiyatu.</p>
        <p xml:lang="en">This is how the confidante informed about [HER] being confined in the house while [HE] was behind the fence.</p>
      </div>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <lg xml:id="NA178">
<l>            āṭamai yākka maitupicain taṉṉa</l>
<l>            tōṭamai tūvit taṭantā ṇārai</l>
<l>            nalaṉuṇap paṭṭa nalkūr pēṭai</l>
<l>            kaḻipeyar maruṅkiṟ ciṟumī ṉuṇṇātu</l>
<l>            kaitaiyam paṭuciṉaip pulampoṭu vatiyun </l>
<l>            taṇṇan tuṟaivaṉ ṟērē kaṇṇiṟ</l>
<l>            kāṇavu miyaintaṉṟu maṉṉē nāṇi</l>
<l>            naḷḷeṉ yāmattuṅ kaṇpaṭai peṟēeṉ</l>
<l>            puḷḷoli maṇiccet tōrppa</l>
<l>            viḷintaṉṟu mātavat teḷintaveṉ ṉeñcē.</l>
            </lg>
       <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The chariot of the man from the cool ghat,</l>
<l rend="indent">where the poor female heron, whose virginity had been consumed</l>
<l rend="indent2">by the broad-footed male, feathers dense in a mass,</l>
<l rend="indent2">just like the nice(?) mass kneaded from the content of the dancing bamboo,</l>
<l rend="indent">abides with loneliness in the swaying Kaitai branch</l>
<l rend="indent">without eating the small fish from the sides of the moving backwaters,</l>
<l>– certainly it was enjoyable just to see it with the eyes.</l>
<l rend="indent4">Full of shame,</l>
<l>I do not obtain sleep even at deepest midnight.</l>
<l>My heart that has gained complete clarity has come to breaking</l>
<l rend="indent">while listening to the sound of the birds, thinking of [his chariot’s] bells.</l>
        </lg>
         </div>
          </body>
